{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6dfe0fa04b","title":"赵紫阳海南放毒记","origin":"","is_range_date":true,"dates":[{"id":"597222b836","index":1,"year":1966,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","article":{}},{"id":"d70c810d03","index":0,"year":1966,"month":2,"day":null,"articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"刘少奇","id":"3aaab89c2a","type":"人物"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"陶铸","id":"dbcf15bd08","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d38f71613f","type":"title","text":"赵紫阳海南放毒记","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6682373143","type":"paragraph","text":"【原编者按：1966年2月下旬，赵紫阳到海南，为期约1个月，跑了14个县，每到一地，则指手划脚，哗啦哗啦，黑话连篇，大放其毒。他鼓吹单干，赞扬自发，提倡金钱挂帅，物质第一，积极为复辟资本主义鸣锣开道。从这些黑话中，赤裸裸的暴露了他的反动咀脸。他说：“社员搞单干有理”；“自发势力的东西也可以学”；“完全是突出政治不成”；“要用钱搞精神，再由精神变物质”；“社会主义吃不饱怎么办？”；“资本主义可以搞的往往是集体经济可以搞的”；“老百姓富了，搞什么都可以了。”等等。这是赵紫阳反党、反社会主义、反毛泽东思想的一次大暴露。","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ccf2d144a9","type":"paragraph","text":"这份材料来自海南区党委印发的记录稿——“随行纪要”。据说，此稿是由当时海南区党委派人跟着赵紫阳逢会必记，有话必录而成。它大抵可以同陶铸的《随行纪谈》相“媲美”。我们从原稿中摘其“精华”，略加整理如下：】","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"09455c63f4","type":"subtitle","text":"2月27日","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"80e2d0aae5","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：澄迈县太平公社塘北大队","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7a7f7584ef","type":"paragraph","text":"1、辱骂贫下中农“无感情”。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6ab4f41e00","type":"paragraph","text":"赵紫阳看到7个社员在一块地里犁田就大发官威：“为什么不一个人犁一块？”社员不理他。赵紫阳就在大队干部座谈会上恶狠狠地说：“我们同他们谈话，好象很无感情，不愿讲就走了。这是什么原因要研究。我看是农民情绪低落”。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"37456c3bda","type":"paragraph","text":"2、攻击群众、干部“无积极性”。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c7ec2c7c7d","type":"paragraph","text":"赵紫阳恨犹未消，又恶狠狠地说：“这里的形势看来是不大好的，群众无劳动的积极性，干部无领导的积极性。”","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3e8ef3ed41","type":"paragraph","text":"3、强令干部向自发势力“学习”。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a8667d6e0a","type":"paragraph","text":"赵紫阳对大队支部书记说：“我对你讲，自发势力也有个好处，为我们开路，他搞什么，我们就搞什么，当然投机倒把不能搞。如他开荒、养鸡，开小片荒地，生产队也可以搞。你不懂就向他学”。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3f51b6a964","type":"subtitle","text":"2月28日","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"62b03fbb98","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：澄迈县委","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e0e0a2c33c","type":"paragraph","text":"4、污蔑毛泽东思想","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2cee76e0b9","type":"paragraph","text":"听了县委汇报后，赵紫阳说：“我们的作风，方针定了，要抓狠。说干就干，一干到底，一次成功。学习毛泽东思想就是抓狠这一条。”","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6b79a4920f","type":"subtitle","text":"3月1日","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"158a6785fa","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：澄迈县镜寨大队","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f157e7749a","type":"paragraph","text":"5、鼓吹金钱挂帅，要下台干部上台。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"09016c6b0b","type":"paragraph","text":"赵紫阳向大队支部书记鼓吹：“要先抓精神，调动积极性。要用钱搞精神，再由精神变物质。这次县开干部会议，要想办法请干部参加，告诉他们你不愿当干部也可以参加一下，上台干部一齐到，发扬民主，告诉他们运动有缺点是要改”。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"70dfe285dc","type":"paragraph","text":"6、鼓吹刘修的《修养》","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"91fc37209a","type":"paragraph","text":"赵紫阳继续对支部书记灌迷魂汤：“在共产党内有时吃亏的事是有的，运动总会出偏差的，但共产党有错就纠，干部要经得起委屈，在困难时不迷失方向，这才是经得起考验的干部”。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5a75760d02","type":"subtitle","text":"3月2日","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"53243b1596","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：澄迈县福山公社","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"599c2ed708","type":"paragraph","text":"7、贩卖赫修福利主义，物质刺激。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2490099a92","type":"paragraph","text":"赵紫阳把福山公社党委书记和红光农场副场长找来，按照“生产第一”的调子吹了一回之后，说：“要给县一点钱，搞点福利，调动大家积极性，主要还是政治挂帅。”","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a049df187d","type":"subtitle","text":"3月3日","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8719d577d7","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：临高县新盈公社","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cdd8de70ff","type":"paragraph","text":"8、散布恐美思想。","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"65adc70b49","type":"paragraph","text":"赵紫阳听了公社党委书记汇报渔业生产情况后，大发谬论：“几年内越南的战争形势是会存在的，大船出深海作业是会受影响的，你们要考虑发展些近海作业。”又说：“由于战争形势，北部港连续出事故，抓走了我们几条船，出深海有些问题，要发展小船，在浅海安全，作业容易……”","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b14c931dd2","type":"paragraph","text":"9、挑拨渔农关系。","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3b2725807d","type":"paragraph","text":"赵紫阳散布了一遍恐美思想之后，接着把矛头转向内部，他说：“你们这里有无渔农关系？”“土改对广东沿海渔民给些田，这是很大的问题，使渔民都搞不好，渔民争地，矛盾很大。”“根本问题是土改时不应给渔民分田，合作化以后矛盾更大。”","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5c9e98c505","type":"paragraph","text":"10、再次鼓吹物质刺激。","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eca2957497","type":"paragraph","text":"赵紫阳对加来农场场长说：“办谷物农场要积极发展多种经营，搞短期收入，长短结合，工资就高，社员就积极了。”“农场一定要给农民一些甜头，要按任务三包，超过了可以奖励。”","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ce8c5dfacc","type":"subtitle","text":"3月4日","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e6f73d1754","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：儋县石屋，侨南大队","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a21aa8aad6","type":"paragraph","text":"11、攻击毛泽东思想。","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b05de9de86","type":"paragraph","text":"赵紫阳参加石屋、侨南（是海南两面红旗）时别有用心地说：“不管你们过去学好了还是没有学好毛主席著作，你们的成绩是毛泽东思想的胜利。你们是自觉不自觉的遵循毛泽东思想的。”","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1eae2636eb","type":"subtitle","text":"3月6日","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bc96984e52","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：昌江县","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a5ebaf0d64","type":"paragraph","text":"12、对抗中央提出的“农业学大寨”的号召。","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9e653c9b1f","type":"paragraph","text":"赵紫阳听了昌江县委汇报开荒造田的情况后，公然说：“现在不需要象河北滚龙庄沟，用1100个劳动日造1亩8分田”。又说：“焦裕禄到兰考的时候很困难，但他就摸自己地区的情况，摸自己的经验，找出自己的道路。他不提学大寨，但他是很好的大寨精神。”","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b4f0185d0e","type":"paragraph","text":"13、根本不想解决“单干”问题。","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1a83ba49ad","type":"paragraph","text":"东方县汇报XX地区基本上是“单干”， 赵紫阳立即说：“一个生产队打口井就巩固了。”","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"09f072caf2","type":"paragraph","text":"14、鼓吹资本主义的物质刺激、金钱第一。","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6ab3b7733b","type":"paragraph","text":"赵紫阳说：“老百姓富了，搞什么都可以了”。","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6ee3569052","type":"subtitle","text":"3月8日","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6177804c3d","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：乐东县","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6fc3d875c7","type":"paragraph","text":"15、鼓吹“单干有理”，搞资本主义复辟。","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4f4434696d","type":"paragraph","text":"赵紫阳听了县委的汇报后狂叫：“除了征购粮，每人平均480斤粮食，既没钱又没粮，所以社员搞单干有道理”。","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3e862ad39a","type":"subtitle","text":"3月9日","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8d9809edc8","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：乐东县","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4669ac6660","type":"paragraph","text":"16、猖狂地反对社会主义，拼命地鼓吹资本主义。","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"885a7a506a","type":"paragraph","text":"赵紫阳在乐东县召开的公社书记座谈会上，赤膊上阵，大放厥词，叫嚷：“自发势力是坏事，但有些可以给集体经济开路，集体搞吃不饱，他们搞就吃饱！”“个人搞的往往是集体经济搞的门路。国营农场先进的经验我们要学，自发势力的东西也可以学。集体经济搞的吃不饱，个人搞的吃得饱。集体分配20斤，个体搞得30斤。”“在商业方面，小商小贩也暴露我们国营商业许多弱点。所以资本主义可以搞的往往是集体经济可以搞的。”“当然，不完全是门路问题，同时是思想问题。总之，老百姓搞不够吃是一个问题。我说，不修水利也应该够吃，资本主义搞够吃就是一个很好的证明。”“你说两条道路是社会主义和资本主义；农民说两条道路，是吃饱和吃不饱。社会主义吃不饱怎么成？”只有20斤原粮，就不好争取多数人搞社会主义。”“年年搞水利，年年50元，年年搞水利，年年吃不饱，你再正确，吃不饱，谁还跟你走？”","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"16d93d55fe","type":"subtitle","text":"3月X日","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f1ff83427b","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：乐东县","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"12a9e1aac5","type":"paragraph","text":"17、攻击社会主义，污蔑贫下中农，攻击党在农村中的阶级路线。","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"624e35425d","type":"paragraph","text":"赵紫阳听了乐东县委的汇报后，挖苦、讽刺说。”一方面统销，一方面出售商品粮，这是尖端材料，一定要依靠水肿病的穷苦的搞两条道路斗争，组织起来。”","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aec0d6d955","type":"subtitle","text":"3月12日","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"da64e6803e","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：保亭县","index":58,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"086c95ec52","type":"paragraph","text":"18、搞资本主义复辟煞费苦心，出谋献策。","index":59,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"924c60c2bc","type":"paragraph","text":"赵紫阳在保亭县召开了公社，农场党委书记会议，借口谈场、社关系问题，提出了一个在农场复辟资本主义的计划，其要点如下：","index":60,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f518fce743","type":"paragraph","text":"第一，推行刘少奇办农场的“三定一奖”办法：定产量，定上交利润，定工资总额，超产奖励。","index":61,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5fea083fd8","type":"paragraph","text":"第二，“你不帮助农民搞到600斤口粮，收入100元，农民是不会积极办场的。……第二年分给每个农民要有150元，这样每个劳动力就有28至30元的工资收入，有这么多的收入，农民收入多了，积极性就会高。","index":62,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"84ffc6ae04","type":"paragraph","text":"第三，“1年800斤根本不要学潮汕，只要一个小型水利，1000斤飞机草，加上除草管理，就可以实现800斤。”","index":63,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1358352783","type":"paragraph","text":"第四，“农民每个月有两次假，就可以喝酒，探亲了。（会上有人反对说：“不习惯。”）习惯要改嘛！”","index":64,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9daf7af831","type":"paragraph","text":"第五，“我想近几年海南可以增加些固定工人，从远江抽一些人来，另外增加些下乡知识青年，退伍兵我主张不增加。”","index":65,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"92bd557d16","type":"subtitle","text":"3月15日","index":66,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8c314c139d","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：崖县榆林","index":67,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f3ddbd1939","type":"paragraph","text":"19、反对突出政治","index":68,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d28d0ae16d","type":"paragraph","text":"赵紫阳在地委书记参加的全省场社结合，财务包干会议上说：“场要搞一点机动权，节约的钱可以用。……当然是也要有一定的机动，搞利润提成；场也有一点机动，可以支援公社，完全是突出政治不成，要场社结合，以场带社。”","index":69,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c3e09046fd","type":"paragraph","text":"20、攻击我国的外贸工作。","index":70,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8c4f0951ea","type":"paragraph","text":"赵紫阳说：“外贸对生产的破坏性大，国际市场需要的拼命搞，所以往往出现这种情况：第一年搞的发大财，第二年搞的还可以，第三年是马马虎虎，第四年的倒霉。”","index":71,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bc1862bc21","type":"subtitle","text":"3月16日","index":72,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eb9741b2b1","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：崖县榆林","index":73,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b726b7f750","type":"paragraph","text":"21、恶毒地攻击毛主席，反对学大庆、学大寨。","index":74,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7a88caed4a","type":"paragraph","text":"在省的场社结合，财务包干会议上，许多同志要求组织去大寨参观。赵紫阳借题发挥，和吴晗、邓拓之流唱和，恶毒地辱骂、攻击毛主席是“皇帝”，说什么“我们都是皇帝的子孙，都在毛主席领导下，为什么我们没有‘大寨’，我们有我们的大庆和大寨，问题是没有发现。”又说：“各地参观可以解放思想，但效果不一定很好，根本的是要找（走）本地的道路，总结本地经验。”","index":75,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"73f05822c9","type":"paragraph","text":"（材料来源：原“市委红旗联络站”）","index":76,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"04973776a1","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：《揭发、批判材料选编（4）》，广州市军管会批陶办公室编，1967年12月28日。","index":77,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"6dfe0fa04b","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}